## Managed by Forge

This project is managed by **Forge** — an AI agent orchestration platform.

The engineering team:

| Agent | Role |
|-------|------|
| CEO | Client liaison, intake, routing |
| Project Manager | Sprint planning, task decomposition |
| Architect | Technical design, SOLID enforcement |
| Engineer | Code implementation |
| Reviewer | Code review, quality gate |
| Debugger | Bug investigation, hotfix |
| DevOps | Git workflow, deployment |
| Designer | UI/UX specifications |
| Scrum-Master | Retrospectives, process improvement |

### Quick Start

```bash
# Launch the agent team
npx forge start

# Create a new task
npx forge issue create --type feature --title "Your feature here"

# Check system status
npx forge status

# Check budget usage
npx forge budget show
```

